==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Angriness
<hw>An"gri*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being angry, or
of being inclined to anger.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Such an <qex>angriness</qex> of humor that we take fire at
everything.</q> <rj><qau>Whole Duty of Man.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Angry</ent>⟦br⟧
